title: Billy Rose's Jumbo [1962 - USA] Doris Day
description:
Billy Rose's Jumbo (1962 - USA)

Comedy / Musical / Romance

starring . . . . Doris Day, Jimmy Durante, Stephen Boyd
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0055797/


Nominated for 1 Oscar with another 8 Award Nominations

The Wonder Circus comes to a town in the Midwest with its featured attraction, Jumbo the elephant. Pop Wonder owns the circus, but his continued gambling losses in crap games leaves the circus with an ever growing number of debts. A warm-hearted MGM musical about circus rivalries, Jumbo is a wonderful film, artistically and technically.
